milestones.description: Holder has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 3 wickets, going past Keith Boyce's 2
Fredericks has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 109 runs, going past Rohan Kanhai's 55
Fredericks's 105 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing Dennis Amiss's 103
Fredericks has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (46) in an innings in ODIs for WI, going past Rohan Kanhai's 26
This is the highest match aggregate (379) involving teams England & West Indies in ODIs
Fredericks's 105 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for WI), surpassing Rohan Kanhai's 55
Keith Boyce has conceded the most runs in an innings (47) in ODIs for WI, going past Keith Boyce's record of 40
Bob Willis has conceded the most runs in an innings (55) in ODIs for ENG, going past Ray Illingworth's record of 50
Fletcher has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for ENG, going past Geoff Boycott
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for WI, going past Foster
Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran's 143-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 125 between Dennis Amiss and Fletcher
Geoff Arnold and Fletcher's 35-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 33 between Saleem Altaf and Wasim Bari
Fletcher has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8), going past Geoff Boycott
Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran's 143-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 125 between Fletcher and Dennis Amiss
Fletcher and Chris Old's 35-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Tony Greig and Chris Old
Geoff Arnold and Fletcher's 35-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Alan Knott and Bob Woolmer
Fredericks and Ron Headley's 43-run partnership is WI's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Fredericks and Foster
Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran's 143-run partnership is WI's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 61 between Rohan Kanhai and Foster
Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran's 143-run partnership is WI's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 61 between Foster and Rohan Kanhai
